{"2996040":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"忍者神龟：破碎命运","steam_appid":2996040,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[3316670,3255900,3247420],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_UnleashTurtlePower_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">喊上几个好友，选择你最喜欢的忍者龟，跃入这款Roguelike冒险之中，从大脚帮的手中救出斯普林特大师！掌握忍者技能，在惊心动魄的在线和本地合作游戏中团结一心，征服纽约各大标志性地区。<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/3.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_BodaciousCoopGameplay_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">在《斯普林特的命运》中，玩家将投身节奏明快的Roguelike动作狂潮之中，没有两次跑酷是完全相同的。强化物品、房间布局和头目增益特效完全随机，精彩刺激享不停。所有四只乌龟都可操控，每只能够驾驭独特的力量，而且还能与好友组队，畅享惊心动魄的合作游戏体验。探索纽约各大标志性的地点，升级乌龟力量，随时准备对抗可怕的敌人。<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/1.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_BuildYourPower_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">掌握水系与火系、奥特姆与奥兹、光明与黑暗的力量，但最重要的是要掌握忍者力量，为忍者龟们打造独特而狂放的组合搭配。每次跑酷都会带来新的挑战和机会，你大可探索和完善自己最喜爱的组合，并与队友默契搭配，共同征服你们的敌人。<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/4.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_AThrillingStory_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">当斯普林特被施瑞德绑架后，整个纽约市同时出现了很多神秘的传送门。为了寻找线索，艾普和金属头对抢回的神器加以分析，乌龟们则展开奋战，誓要从大脚帮的魔掌中救回他们的父亲。然而，随着大伙儿距离斯普林特所处的异界位置越来越近，一个更大的威胁却从阴影之中浮现出来……<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/4.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">针对PC做出额外的设置、平衡和微调强化后，《斯普林特的命运》必定让你沉浸其中，不断开启战斗、适应、重复的传送门循环。快做好准备，恢复这座城市往日的和平吧！<\/p>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_UnleashTurtlePower_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">喊上几个好友，选择你最喜欢的忍者龟，跃入这款Roguelike冒险之中，从大脚帮的手中救出斯普林特大师！掌握忍者技能，在惊心动魄的在线和本地合作游戏中团结一心，征服纽约各大标志性地区。<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/3.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_BodaciousCoopGameplay_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">在《斯普林特的命运》中，玩家将投身节奏明快的Roguelike动作狂潮之中，没有两次跑酷是完全相同的。强化物品、房间布局和头目增益特效完全随机，精彩刺激享不停。所有四只乌龟都可操控，每只能够驾驭独特的力量，而且还能与好友组队，畅享惊心动魄的合作游戏体验。探索纽约各大标志性的地点，升级乌龟力量，随时准备对抗可怕的敌人。<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/1.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/TMNTSF_SteamHeaderImage_BuildYourPower_CN.png?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">掌握水系与火系、奥特姆与奥兹、光明与黑暗的力量，但最重要的是要掌握忍者力量，为忍者龟们打造独特而狂放的组合搭配。每次跑酷都会带来新的挑战和机会，你大可探索和完善自己最喜爱的组合，并与队友默契搭配，共同征服你们的敌人。<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2996040\/extras\/4.gif?t=1747920147\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\